{
  "title": "Continuing Education, Now More Convenient Than Ever!",
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"hero__container hero__container--small hero__container--no-image\" data-hero-container=\"\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<div class=\"hero__text-container hero__text-container--center hero__text-container__small\">\n<h1 class=\"u-font-family-secondary hero__title\">Continuing Education, Now More Convenient Than Ever! </h1>\n</div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Meeting your continuing education requirements just got easier. CEU Mobile allows insurance producers and adjusters to complete approved CE courses from any device — laptop, tablet, or smartphone.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container media-block__container--reversed\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"Hand holding cell phone that features the CEU Mobile app\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2026-03/landing-page-ceu-app-800x533.png?itok=RqMjDuMk\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2026-03/landing-page-ceu-app-800x533.png?itok=RqMjDuMk 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned_2x/public/2026-03/landing-page-ceu-app-800x533.png?itok=jsDo3T7Y  2x\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__header\">\n<h2 class=\"u-margin-hug-top\">\n            Complete Approved CE Courses from Any Device\n          </h2>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__content\">\n<p><a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/ceu/ceu-unlimited\">CEU Unlimited subscribers</a> can access our full library of <a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/ceu/course-search\">150+ on-demand courses</a> covering required topics such as ethics, NFIP, and state-specific CE requirements through CEU Mobile.</p><p>Now, enjoy even greater flexibility with CEU Unlimited: </p><ul><li>Start a course on your laptop and finish on your phone</li><li>Complete entire courses on your mobile device</li><li>24/7 access to approved continuing education courses</li><li>Seamless login — no app download required </li></ul><p>Whether you're between client meetings, traveling, or working remotely, CEU Mobile gives you convenient access to the CE hours you need to stay compliant.</p><p>This is in addition to CEU’s existing benefits, giving you an unmatched experience and easing the burden of meeting your CE requirements: </p><ul><li>No state reporting fees</li><li>No hidden fees</li><li>Unlimited exam retakes</li><li>CE credit hours reported within two business days</li><li>One flat annual price </li></ul>\n</div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><h2>Access CEU Mobile today and take your CE on the go.</h2><p>For convenient access we recommend adding this page or <a href=\"https://ceu.theinstitutes.org/\">the CEU Mobile sign in page</a> to your home screen.  </p><p> </p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<div class=\"container__grid container__grid--centered container__grid--max-md\">\n<div class=\"u-text-center\">\n<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<hr aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hr hr--centered hr--md hr--light\" role=\"presentation\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"u-padding-top u-padding-bottom container__grid\">\n<ul class=\"u-list-unstyled\" data-aria-accordion=\"\" data-default=\"none\" role=\"tablist\">\n<li class=\"accordion__item\" role=\"tab\">\n<p class=\"u-margin-hug\" data-aria-accordion-heading=\"\">\n     Do I need to download an app? \n    </p>\n<div data-aria-accordion-panel=\"\">\n<p>No, just add this page or the <a href=\"https://ceu.theinstitutes.org/\" target=\"_blank\">CEU Mobile sign in page</a> to your home screen for easy access to your CE courses.</p>\n</div>\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"accordion__icon\" height=\"40\" role=\"presentation\" viewbox=\"0 0 40 40\" width=\"40\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M20,4c8.8,0,16,7.2,16,16s-7.2,16-16,16S4,28.8,4,20S11.2,4,20,4 M20,0C9,0,0,9,0,20s9,20,20,20s20-9,20-20 S31,0,20,0L20,0z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path><rect fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"4\" width=\"22\" x=\"9\" y=\"18\"></rect><rect class=\"accordion__icon-vertical-bar\" fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"22\" width=\"4\" x=\"18\" y=\"9\"></rect></svg>\n</li>\n\n<li class=\"accordion__item\" role=\"tab\">\n<p class=\"u-margin-hug\" data-aria-accordion-heading=\"\">\n     Can I complete courses entirely on my phone?\n    </p>\n<div data-aria-accordion-panel=\"\">\n<p>Yes! Start a course on your laptop and finish on your phone, or complete entire courses on your mobile device.</p>\n</div>\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"accordion__icon\" height=\"40\" role=\"presentation\" viewbox=\"0 0 40 40\" width=\"40\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M20,4c8.8,0,16,7.2,16,16s-7.2,16-16,16S4,28.8,4,20S11.2,4,20,4 M20,0C9,0,0,9,0,20s9,20,20,20s20-9,20-20 S31,0,20,0L20,0z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path><rect fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"4\" width=\"22\" x=\"9\" y=\"18\"></rect><rect class=\"accordion__icon-vertical-bar\" fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"22\" width=\"4\" x=\"18\" y=\"9\"></rect></svg>\n</li>\n\n<li class=\"accordion__item\" role=\"tab\">\n<p class=\"u-margin-hug\" data-aria-accordion-heading=\"\">\n     Are CE credit hours reported the same way?\n    </p>\n<div data-aria-accordion-panel=\"\">\n<p>Yes, regardless of device used to complete your course CE credit hours are reported within two business days.</p>\n</div>\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"accordion__icon\" height=\"40\" role=\"presentation\" viewbox=\"0 0 40 40\" width=\"40\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M20,4c8.8,0,16,7.2,16,16s-7.2,16-16,16S4,28.8,4,20S11.2,4,20,4 M20,0C9,0,0,9,0,20s9,20,20,20s20-9,20-20 S31,0,20,0L20,0z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path><rect fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"4\" width=\"22\" x=\"9\" y=\"18\"></rect><rect class=\"accordion__icon-vertical-bar\" fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"22\" width=\"4\" x=\"18\" y=\"9\"></rect></svg>\n</li>\n\n<li class=\"accordion__item\" role=\"tab\">\n<p class=\"u-margin-hug\" data-aria-accordion-heading=\"\">\n     Is there an additional cost to use CEU Mobile?\n    </p>\n<div data-aria-accordion-panel=\"\">\n<p>That’s the best part! No! Access to CEU Mobile is included in your CEU Unlimited subscription for no additional fee.</p>\n</div>\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"accordion__icon\" height=\"40\" role=\"presentation\" viewbox=\"0 0 40 40\" width=\"40\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M20,4c8.8,0,16,7.2,16,16s-7.2,16-16,16S4,28.8,4,20S11.2,4,20,4 M20,0C9,0,0,9,0,20s9,20,20,20s20-9,20-20 S31,0,20,0L20,0z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path><rect fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"4\" width=\"22\" x=\"9\" y=\"18\"></rect><rect class=\"accordion__icon-vertical-bar\" fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"22\" width=\"4\" x=\"18\" y=\"9\"></rect></svg>\n</li>\n\n<li class=\"accordion__item\" role=\"tab\">\n<p class=\"u-margin-hug\" data-aria-accordion-heading=\"\">\n     I’m having trouble saving this to my home screen, can you help me?\n    </p>\n<div data-aria-accordion-panel=\"\">\n<p>Yes! Follow these <a href=\"https://web.theinstitutes.org/sites/default/files/2026-03/ceu-mobile-instructions-2026.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">step-by-step instructions</a> to save CEU Mobile to your home screen.</p>\n</div>\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"accordion__icon\" height=\"40\" role=\"presentation\" viewbox=\"0 0 40 40\" width=\"40\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M20,4c8.8,0,16,7.2,16,16s-7.2,16-16,16S4,28.8,4,20S11.2,4,20,4 M20,0C9,0,0,9,0,20s9,20,20,20s20-9,20-20 S31,0,20,0L20,0z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path><rect fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"4\" width=\"22\" x=\"9\" y=\"18\"></rect><rect class=\"accordion__icon-vertical-bar\" fill=\"currentColor\" height=\"22\" width=\"4\" x=\"18\" y=\"9\"></rect></svg>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container media-block__container--reversed\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"A pink piggy bank swims cutely in a bath of gold coins. \" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=bMmCvybb\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=bMmCvybb 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned_2x/public/2023-05/Pig_In_Gold.jpg?itok=wzo3tkhj  2x\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__header\">\n<h2 class=\"u-margin-hug\">\n            Not a CEU Unlimited Subscriber?\n          </h2>\n<hr aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hr hr--offset hr--md hr--md--offset hr--light\" role=\"presentation\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__content\">\n<p>Get 12 months of unlimited access to 150+ on-demand courses and live webinars approved for Property &amp; Casualty and Life &amp; Health licenses all for one flat annual price. </p><p><strong>Get CEU Unlimited – Just $85 a Year!</strong></p>\n<a class=\"u-margin-top btn btn--secondary\" href=\"/ceu/ceu-unlimited\" title=\"Get CEU Unlimited Today!\">Get CEU Unlimited Today!</a>\n</div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div></body></html>",
